{"fadeType":2,"once":true,"scripts":[{"mode":1,"stopbgm":true,"sequence":[["The Lucky Crane\n\n<size=45>Chapter 2 - Zuikaku & Her Friends<\/size>",1]]},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"side":2,"say":"After Zuikaku hurriedly gave me her morning report, we went out together for a walk around the base.","dir":1,"bgName":"bg_story_outdoor","bgm":"story-1"},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"Sorry, Commander... I was up all night cramming Offense Skillbooks...","dir":1,"actorName":"{namecode:96}","side":2,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"bgName":"bg_story_outdoor","actor":307060},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"... I know, I'll be more careful next time...","dir":1,"actorName":"{namecode:96}","side":2,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"bgName":"bg_story_outdoor","actor":307060},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"Hey, what's this? Why's everyone gathering at the pier?","dir":1,"actorName":"{namecode:96}","side":2,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"bgName":"bg_story_outdoor","actor":307060},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","paintingFadeOut":{"side":0,"time":0.5},"say":"Why, if it ain't Zuikaku! You out for a walk with the Commander?","dir":1,"actorName":"{namecode:76}","side":1,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"bgName":"bg_story_outdoor","actor":305030},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"Yup! So, why are you all gathered here?","dir":1,"actorName":"{namecode:96}","side":0,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"bgName":"bg_story_outdoor","actor":307060},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"We wanted to talk to some Eagle Union peeps about a joint exercise, and we're discussing how to bring it up with them.","dir":1,"actorName":"{namecode:77}","side":1,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"bgName":"bg_story_outdoor","actor":305040},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"Uh, can't you just, like, bring it up with them? Like normal people do?","dir":1,"actorName":"{namecode:96}","side":0,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"bgName":"bg_story_outdoor","actor":307060},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"Ise and Hyuuga could maybe do it, but most of us aren't the types who can just ask someone about a joint exercise...","dir":1,"actorName":"{namecode:47}","side":1,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"bgName":"bg_story_outdoor","actor":302090},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"She's right. If someone like Takao or I were to ask them, we'd come off as too formal, and they might speculate that we're up to something...","dir":-1,"actorName":"{namecode:54}","side":1,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"bgName":"bg_story_outdoor","actor":303020},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"Then why don't I do it? I was just about to head their way anyhow.","dir":1,"actorName":"{namecode:96}","side":0,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"bgName":"bg_story_outdoor","actor":307060},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"Really? 'Cause that'd be a huge help.","dir":1,"actorName":"{namecode:76}","side":1,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"bgName":"bg_story_outdoor","actor":305030},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"If Zuikaku will ask on our behalf, then I'm sure it'll go well.","dir":1,"actorName":"{namecode:47}","side":1,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"bgName":"bg_story_outdoor","actor":302090},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"Yeah. Sorry for making you go out of your way like this, Zuikaku.","dir":-1,"actorName":"{namecode:54}","side":1,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"bgName":"bg_story_outdoor","actor":303020},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"No need to be sorry! I can handle it, no problem!","dir":1,"actorName":"{namecode:96}","side":0,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"bgName":"bg_story_outdoor","actor":307060},{"flashout":{"dur":1,"alpha":[0,1],"black":true},"side":2,"say":"Zuikaku went to the Eagle Union dormitory and proposed the joint exercise. Almost everybody she told about it agreed to participate.","dir":1,"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"bgName":"bg_story_outdoor","flashin":{"delay":1,"dur":1,"alpha":[1,0],"black":true}},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"*Phew*... That about makes it one lap around the base, huh?","dir":1,"actorName":"{namecode:96}","side":2,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"bgName":"bg_story_outdoor","actor":307060},{"typewriter":{"speedUp":0.01,"speed":0.05},"nameColor":"#a9f548","say":"This happens surprisingly often~ Like, I'm just out and about, then suddenly somebody asks me for a favor.","dir":1,"actorName":"{namecode:96}","side":2,"painting":{"time":1,"alpha":0.3},"actor":307060,"bgName":"bg_story_outdoor","blackBg":true}],"mode":2,"fadein":1.5,"id":"RUIHE2","fadeOut":1.5}